{"tid":1596284,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"食食下加藤屋 有人放催淚彈","createTime":"2019-09-26T12:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T22:51:01.000Z","uid":92255,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5707494ee31e39f4cc27e459f2e61f20cc0d61ff","tid":1596284,"uid":92255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:40:34.000Z","msg":"今日去長沙灣食嘢 搭枱坐<br />\n見到兩個著住校服嘅細路<br />\n目測中三中四左右<br />\n聽到佢哋屌吉野家已經覺得好神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知講講下突然間講到買文具<br />\n又話啲文具百幾蚊 唔捨得買<br />\n又偷聽到佢哋講話啲牛鬼蛇神好惡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到我食食下飯喺度留馬尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底香港做錯啲咩 要班細路咁樣生活<br />\n要香港人承受依家呢種局面<br />\n<br />\n最後本來想叫男朋友關心下<br />\n始終發惡夢對小朋友心理好大影響<br />\n屌 點知我哋銀包得返$150<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係唔好意思 希望你哋夠用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw下次喺條街度記得唔好咁大聲討論夢境<br />\n如果下次撞著係衰人就慘<br />\n同埋電話唔夠容量好慘<br />\n記得定期刪相 刪wtsapp記錄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 希望大家能夠煲底相見 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望你哋萬事平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3433ff5638b01d998d1600df948b787fc44561e","tid":1596284,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就黎變飯堂<br />\n下次想助養兒童可以去食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ea7da95c0e3e1eb1ef83e65edb31059004008d","tid":1596284,"uid":92255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3433ff5638b01d998d1600df948b787fc44561e","tid":1596284,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就黎變飯堂<br />\n下次想助養兒童可以去食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:54:46.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你偷聽下就搵到"},{"pid":"d55a39b95098df2a8ba5fa79c8ea79fb49f71f60","tid":1596284,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07ea7da95c0e3e1eb1ef83e65edb31059004008d","tid":1596284,"uid":92255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3433ff5638b01d998d1600df948b787fc44561e","tid":1596284,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就黎變飯堂<br />\n下次想助養兒童可以去食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:54:46.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你偷聽下就搵到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要翻屋食劣食"},{"pid":"2d3d82e7625fe2f3d68ea7372a57d8f43878c193","tid":1596284,"uid":87610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:59:00.000Z","msg":"叫啲小朋友唔好咁大聲公開講<br />\n唔係個個咁啱遇到你啲好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340aad490ad96d8a05a789c7b2c78b7b0fdc66a4","tid":1596284,"uid":92255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d3d82e7625fe2f3d68ea7372a57d8f43878c193","tid":1596284,"uid":87610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:59:00.000Z","msg":"叫啲小朋友唔好咁大聲公開講<br />\n唔係個個咁啱遇到你啲好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T22:47:45.000Z","msg":"擔心兩個小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8524bd09cab0da9cd9599edfe455dcafcdcbaf6e","tid":1596284,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T22:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.g